name: Intacto14
author: Anubi
description:
The
 palette I'm using nowadays for my pixel arts, 14 colors distributed 
along 5 color ramps (Gray, Green, Blue, Red, Brown), aiming to be 
flexible in many circunstances, while still not having way too many 
colors. The most common colors were picked for this palette, which 
should cover most of your ideas.
